---

Load fixture data into the database. Run automatically for integration tests.

### Syntax

```
$ vela fixtures load
```

This will load fixture data into the database from the `data/fixtures` directory. Fixtures are loaded in alphabetical order and prefixed with a number to ensure deterministic loading order.
